        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued July 28 at 6:25PM PDT by NWS Pendleton OR</headline>
        <description>At 625 PM PDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm 7
miles west of Three Rivers, or 11 miles northwest of La Pine, moving
northwest at 15 mph.

HAZARD...Half inch hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor hail damage to vegetation is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Three Rivers.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
